name: Alexander Dahl
cooked: While AOI seems quite common for professional manufacturers, at least according to the Wikipedia Page about it, I could not find any open projects doing it. Is anyone aware of open hard- or software for AOI?
raw: While AOI seems quite common for professional manufacturers, at least according to the [Wikipedia Page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Automated_optical_inspection) about it, I could not find any open projects doing it. Is anyone aware of open hard- or software for AOI?
